snippet.title: Amber Heard Is Going After Johnny Depp's Son on Social Media (SHOCKING)
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Is Going After Johnny Depp's Son on Social Media (SHOCKING)

Join us in today’s video as we share with you how Amber Heard threatened Johnny Depp’s son on social media. Being in Hollywood must be the dream come true. From the glitz to the glam, you can never go wrong, especially when you meet and marry another celebrity. But this isn’t the case for Amber Heard and Johnny Depp, as the two are still facing a lot of issues against them.

Recently, old texts showing the violence of Amber Heard towards Johnny Depp resurfaced on the Web. Since their separation in 2016, the two exes have been talked about a lot and the trial with The Sun, judging the actor of Pirates of the Caribbean of “wife batter” only made matters worse. And in these messages, Johnny Depp’s son has exposed Amber Heard. Be sure to watch the whole video and see the whole story! In addition, do us a favor and like the video and subscribe and turn on the notification bell. We’ll see you in the next video!
